                  <summary><p>A medical treatise. By a Christian copyist (see Christian cross on U1, f[1]r, c1).</p>
<p>The bundle was in disorder when examined (2021-10). Reordered then by E. Francis. The bundle is also in disorder and inversed on the BnF microfilm.</p>
<p>Description based on the examination of the original manuscript (October 2021).</p>
   <p>Dimensions assessed at the time of examination.</p> 
